### 5. Configure .gitignore

Edit `.gitignore`:
```
# Virtual Environment
venv/
env/

# Environment Variables
.env

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

# Temporary Files
temp_files/*
!temp_files/.gitkeep

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Generated Files
*.pdf
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.ics